{
  "texts": [
    "BiRSwinT employs a dual-stream structure to process and analyze various data types, performing exceptionally well on the AUC V1 and V2 datasets.",
    "This dual-stream design allows for the simultaneous processing of global and local cues of driver actions, enhancing the detection of subtle behaviors and improving the overall safety of autonomous vehicles [69,89,91].Another highly accurate system for detecting driver distraction consists of a blend of deep learning and machine learning models, fine-tuned by a genetic algorithm.",
    "This system adapts to new datasets in real-time, aiming to enhance traffic precautions through the Hybrid Genetic Deep Network.",
    "This model uses principles from genetic algorithms and deep neural networks.",
    "It utilizes evolutionary techniques to optimize the architecture and processes of deep learning networks."
  ]
}